snippet.title: Best VGM 1093 - Jack Bros. - Temple of Nightmare
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2082 - https://youtu.be/GaOT77kUTD8

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Virtual Boy
Jack Bros. (1995)
Temple of Nightmare
Hiroyuki Yanada
